    subtitle="Here are some recommended options for buying and selling Bitcoin Cash BCH. Act with care, use reputable exchanges and be sure to hold your coins securely. It is not recommended to leave your coins on centralized exchanges indefinitely."
    highlight="Buy some BCH"
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Coinbase',
        description:
          'Global',
        icon: 'https://static.panmoni.org/bitcoincashsite/coinbase.png',
        url: 'https://www.coinbase.com/',
      },
      {
        title: 'Binance',
